; Regression test for issue #1112: --debug does not work with equal sign (BZ#1112)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/1112
; The --debug=CATEGORY form (using = instead of space) should be accepted
; without error and produce normal output.

2024/01/01 Groceries
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test --debug=parser bal
             $-10.00  Assets:Cash
              $10.00  Expenses:Food
--------------------
                   0
end test
